Author: pbca26#5430
Content:
been playing a bit with telegram bot api today
wrote my first bot that can check kmd rewards and send notifications if 1 month period is passed or utxos are not generating rewards

Usage examples (or type /help):
/rewards RDPSgU4kmr3Xq3WSfWdeP5wah7HSP8tdsS
/rewards-subscribe RDPSgU4kmr3Xq3WSfWdeP5wah7HSP8tdsS
/rewards-unsubscribe RDPSgU4kmr3Xq3WSfWdeP5wah7HSP8tdsS

Once an address is subscribed rewards are checked every day. Notifications are sent out every day if the above conditions are met. If not met no notifications.

it's a really quick write up at this point so excuse any annoying tg messages if things go wrong
any bug reports are welcomed and will help me polish everything

bot's user name @kmd_rewards_notifications_bot
